er with 50pp but then you would be in total shock when that 1k you had in the bank went to the gem merchants. Oh another note, if you sell everything back as you go you will not have to return to the bank until you are done. If you want more information or a Trivial Chart check out <br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/tradeskills/tradeskills.asp">eq.castersrealm.com/trade...skills.asp</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br><br>Hope this helps,<br><br>Sam<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://homepage.mac.com/mcrisefi/.Pictures/sam-pony-1-2.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>Guild Mistress, The Crusaders of the High Plains <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1571.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1571.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1571.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1571.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.threadControl?topicID=1571.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1571.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclear